Citation.sAbstract: A new apparatus for the determination of VLE has been constructed which works for absolute pressure  measurements as well as for measuring differential pressures. The first results obtained are (vapor + liquid)  equilibria (VLE) of binary mixtures containing acetonitrile or tetrahydrofuran and the ionic liquid (IL) 1-ethyl-3-methylimidazolium bis(trifluoromethylsulfonyl)imide [EMIm][NTf2] by using the absolute pressures method. VLE measurements were carried out over the whole concentration range at four different temperatures between 293.15 K and 313.15 K. Activity coefficients of the solvents in  [EMIm][NTf2] and their osmotic coefficients have been determined from the VLE data.
Citation.sTitle: Vapor pressures and activity coefficients of binary mixtures of 1-ethyl-3-methylimidazolium bis(trifluoromethylsulfonyl)imide  with acetonitrile and tetrahydrofuran
